{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"element-available","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/element-available","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>element-available</code> 関数は、要素が利用可能かどうかを判断し、true または false を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">element-available(<em>QName</em> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"qname\"><code><em>QName</em></code></dt>\n <dd>有効な QName を評価する必要があります。QName は式のスコープ内の名前空間宣言を使用して展開された名前に展開されます。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>展開された名前が命令の名前である場合にのみ true を返します。展開された名前が XSLT 名前空間 URI と等しい名前空間 URI を持つ場合、XSLT&nbsp; で定義された要素を参照します。それ以外の場合は拡張要素を参照します。展開された名前が null の名前空間 URI を持つ場合、要素利用可能な関数は false を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xslt#function-element-available\" rel=\" noopener\">XSLT 1.0 15</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko のサポート","isH3":true,"content":"<p>サポート済み</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"element-available 関数は、要素が利用可能かどうかを判断し、true または false を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"element-available","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"element-available","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"element-available","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element-available","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/element-available","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/element-available/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/element-available","title":"element-available"}],"pageTitle":"element-available - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}